 "headline": "Planted-truth synthetic lab: the EXACT validated channels (WP3.1 position C/V + WP3.2 substitution + WP5 seed bootstrap) RECOVER the planted C/V+morphology at LB token-scale (position AUC 0.778, WP5 seed AUC 0.677, substitution significant 100% of runs) and REJECT a wrong-language corpus with dense pseudo-cognates (position AUC 0.497, CI upper 0.642). The SAME planted language at LA scale (4245 tokens, LA-style packing) returns NO_POWER: position AUC CI [0.427, 0.720] and substitution significant only 0% of runs - a CALIBRATED FAILURE, not a false positive. Recovery (AUC>=0.75) needs >=8000 tokens word-segmented (~1.88x LA); LA's null is therefore corpus-power-limited, not a broken method.",
 "verdict_gate_note": "Positive-control gate = WP3.1 position AUC>=0.75 AND WP3.2 substitution firing (>=50% of runs vs degree-preserving null). WP5 clean-seed AUC is intrinsically modest (unsupervised floor ~0.5, supervised ceiling ~0.83) so it is NOT gated at 0.75; it must instead show the size-gradient (LB 0.677 > LA 0.548 > wrong 0.491), which it does. An earlier gate that hard-required WP5 LB>=0.75 returned NO_POWER solely because WP5 LB landed at 0.677 (<0.75) under mc_reps=12 variance, while position (0.778) and substitution (100%) recovered decisively."
